              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Targets were bombarded by the 65 MeV helium",
                "ions in Berkeley, California. The targets were then",
                "flown to the laboratories in Bellingham where the",
                "fission fragments were separated by standard",
                "radiochemical techniques. The period of time between",
                "the end of bombardment to the time when counting of",
                "the radiochemically separated species began, was",
                "about l0 h."
              ]
            }
